{"tid":2412291,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪有好多人唔知對家出緊大量離間計","createTime":"2021-02-18T02:55:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-18T11:40:16.000Z","uid":358549,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"597e4e2685eec2790391fc05a5c8d74f35ab0554","tid":2412291,"uid":358549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:55:50.000Z","msg":"本身有二百萬人<br />\n對家入城帶風向  <br />\n話邊個唔夠黃 就成班人屌走佢哋<br />\n整宣誓<br />\n邊個宣誓 就同律政司/警隊/國安一樣仆街 又有D人離隊<br />\n遲D區會宣誓 又屌走埋D區議員 發聲空間又縮細<br />\n下年搞埋中資 醫院 公營機構 地鐵<br />\n<br />\n無論係陣營人數定係資源都慢慢俾人用離間削弱得好緊要<br />\n到最尾得番幾十萬人 就俾人帶風向做乜交稅俾錢人經營國安 又逼走D人 一係移民一係以後都收埋自己唔講野<br />\n<br />\n最尾香港無晒人 嗰陣點打？<br />\n<br />\n希望依個陣營可以正面少少"},{"pid":"876d6b0ed493754fefb5df6b751b6d10342771d8","tid":2412291,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"陳雲一早講左  <br />\n<br />\n戴口罩係用來批鬥人<br />\n<br />\n你地唔信死都要戴<br />\n<br />\n怪邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128ec2c90ddb21a0c8f4f463bec889c1381bdf29","tid":2412291,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"蘋果仲要維穩"},{"pid":"266d6a0a65291f22bf82a521df4bfc39bd893751","tid":2412291,"uid":358549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"推.."},{"pid":"e0ffa7383201cb679c767e29b4275493c78608a2","tid":2412291,"uid":171107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"876d6b0ed493754fefb5df6b751b6d10342771d8","tid":2412291,"uid":228143,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T02:56:59.000Z","msg":"陳雲一早講左  <br />\n<br />\n戴口罩係用來批鬥人<br />\n<br />\n你地唔信死都要戴<br />\n<br />\n怪邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-18T07:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3f55opO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3f55opO.jpg&h=d95a3a17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b1489339973e30333d